726885f-a.text:
Hollis Ave. (foreground), at the S.W. corner of 102nd Street, showing in a set of two views the David Purdy house thereon. 0ther owners were C. Mott, 1860; D. J. Purdy, 1873-1891; amd two sisters
and a brother of David S. Purdy in 1934.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

726880f-a.text:
Hollis Ave., east side, opposite 1O2nd Ave., showing fully the A. Oakley Eetcham house. D. Eetcham and E. Mason were the
